    <section class="slide">
        <h2>How we achieved SDL proposed design </h2>
		<ul><li>We needed to have different formats for input. We concluded that we can convert graph into different formats like, rdf/xml, rdfa, turtle, json-ld.</li>
		<li>Now we have all these formats, there is just a need to modify linter views.</li>
		<li>As the implementation of views is in key/value paris like,
		<code>{"snippet": "...", "html": "...", "messages": [], "statistics": {"count": 9, "templates": []}}</code>
		We passed "rdf":"rdfformat", "rdfa": "rdfaformat", "ttl": "ttlformat", "jsonld": jsonldformat", "graph": graphformat".</li>
		<li>For graph, we currenly use http://www.ldf.fi/service/rdf-grapher API.</li></ul></p>
    </section>

